            <title>[LUDOC-141] Client Read-Write Offset Survey</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-141</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre 2.x manual, section:&lt;br/&gt;
31.2.3. Client Read-Write Offset Survey&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Shows the file in question to be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;cat /proc/fs/lustre/llite/lustre-f57dee00/rw_offset_stats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;File on a 1.8.9 system is:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;cat /proc/fs/lustre/llite/lustre-f57dee00/offset_stats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Need to determine if this is a documentation issue or a Lustre version issue.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
